OL,7,FITV Granada's Andrew Fletcher spoke to
OL,8,Fresidents in Bacup about the council's
OL,9,Fplans.
OL,11,FResidents in Bacup are protesting
OL,12,Fagainst Rossendale Council's plans to
OL,13,Fbuild a new 50,000-tonne-a-year-
OL,14,Fcapacity waste disposal unit in the
OL,15,Ftown centre.
OL,17,FThere is already a waste transfer site
OL,18,Fon the proposed location but the new
OL,19,Fbuilding is due to be bigger.
