OL,7,FCharlie Codd's back garden directly
OL,8,Ffaces the disposal unit and says he
OL,9,Fhas got used to the sights, sounds and
OL,10,Fsmells of the waste site.
OL,12,FBut the council's plans are causing
OL,13,Fnew worries for him and his neighbours.
OL,15,F"There are a large concentration of
OL,16,Fhouses that will be affected by odour,
OL,17,Fbut also contaminated dust", Charlie
OL,18,Fsaid.
