OL,7,FHe added: "They (the council) have
OL,8,Fsaid that the odour will be in low
OL,9,Fwind condition and the contminated
OL,10,Fdust will be in worse in high wind
OL,11,Fconditions.
OL,13,F"In other words, whatever the wind
OL,14,Fconditions are, we'll be getting it
OL,15,Fone way or another."
OL,17,FThe Henrietta Street site is used for
OL,18,Fcollecting and sorting recyclable
OL,19,Fwaste.
