OL,7,FThe council's proposing a new waste
OL,8,Ftransfer building at the site, which
OL,9,Fwill allow it to meet a Government
OL,10,Frequirement to collect food waste
OL,11,Fseparately from other household waste.
OL,13,FBut residents fear the plans will lead
OL,14,Fto more lorries delivering and
OL,15,Fcollecting waste from the site - and
OL,16,Fmore disruption to their lives.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
