OL,7,FLynda Melvin who lives nearby said
OL,8,F"The smells, the flies, the rats,
OL,9,Fwhich we've already had, and what it's
OL,10,Fgoing to do to the town centre, it's
OL,11,Fsupposed to be a heritage town and
OL,12,Fthey are doing all these improvements.
OL,14,F"We have Bacup Pride, Cleaning all up,
OL,15,Fand it's just going to be worse than
OL,16,Fever."JResidents made their feelings
OL,17,Fknown at a peaceful protest outside
OL,18,Fthe council office on Friday 3rd
OL,19,FJanuary.
