OL,7,FRossendale council has defended the
OL,8,Fplans, insisting they won't lead to
OL,9,Fany increase in the amount of waste it
OL,10,Fhandles.
OL,12,FCouncillor Alyson Barnes, Leader,
OL,13,FRossendale Council said " We're not
OL,14,Fchanging anything, we're still going
OL,15,Fto be processing the same waste from
OL,16,Fthe same households. We're just going
OL,17,Fto be sorting it differently.
OL,19,F"I would like to reassure residents
OL,20,Fthat we are looking to improve what
OL,21,Fthey are already.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
