OL,7,F"Currently, the whole site is open to
OL,8,Fthe elements, if we encase this in a
OL,9,Fbuilding state the outlook will be
OL,10,Fimproved, but I think the general
OL,11,Fexperience will be improved as well.
OL,12,FIt won't be as messy and as smelly as
OL,13,Fit currently is."
